an interesting aspect of it

43:17.820 --> 43:19.820
oh very interesting

43:19.820 --> 43:20.820
yeah

43:20.820 --> 43:27.820
and did you hear independently anything about the material being sort of aluminum foil like

43:27.820 --> 43:30.820
or you know if you crumple it up it goes back into its original position

43:30.820 --> 43:32.820
no the only thing I heard was people

43:32.820 --> 43:34.820
first hand witnesses I personally interviewed

43:34.820 --> 43:38.820
and it said it was cylindrical shaped like a school bus

43:38.820 --> 43:39.820
like a cigar

43:39.820 --> 43:41.820
had no control services that kind of thing

43:41.820 --> 43:43.820
and another interesting aspect of it

43:43.820 --> 43:47.820
is Dr. Armando who did the autopsy on the deceased military officer

43:47.820 --> 43:48.820
he

43:48.820 --> 43:49.820
has two friends

43:49.820 --> 43:50.820
farmers

43:50.820 --> 43:53.820
that saw exactly what he saw before it crashed

43:53.820 --> 43:55.820
just another little piece

43:55.820 --> 43:56.820
yeah

43:56.820 --> 43:57.820
the puzzle

43:57.820 --> 44:00.820
there's so many aspects of this story

44:00.820 --> 44:01.820
well you also have

44:01.820 --> 44:02.820
farmers

44:02.820 --> 44:04.820
documented in moment of contact

44:04.820 --> 44:06.820
you also have a guy who looked outside his window

44:06.820 --> 44:07.820
yes

44:07.820 --> 44:08.820
looking at it

44:08.820 --> 44:10.820
and then you show the entire flight path

44:10.820 --> 44:11.820
yes

44:11.820 --> 44:12.820
and then I think what I love

44:12.820 --> 44:16.820
to be honest about Carlos de Sosa's testimony specifically

44:16.820 --> 44:19.820
is you have this very dramatic part of moment of contact

44:19.820 --> 44:22.820
where he's showing you the site the crash site

44:23.820 --> 44:27.820
and to me if you were a liar he would have said here it is

44:27.820 --> 44:31.820
but he gets there and he goes it wasn't here in fact the landscape has changed

44:31.820 --> 44:36.820
and he goes I'm looking for this white house I swear it's a white house it's a white house

44:36.820 --> 44:39.820
and he took you for two hours

44:39.820 --> 45:08.820
yeah I thought this was the I was so disappointed at the time I was like oh my god this is going horribly how could this guy not remember where the spot was and and and then when he sees the actual spot not only do you see different topology and vegetation a different color coloration of the ground locally where he says the spot is but he starts crying and you this is very moving part of the movie where you say a key a key and you break down

45:08.820 --> 45:13.820
and uh I don't know I don't think you can fake that so

45:13.820 --> 45:37.820
yeah it's pretty I mean you have to ask yourself you know why witnesses come forward he's not selling a book he's not selling a documentary we chased him down we found him Marco Leal found him chased him down and he finally agreed to meet with me and then he ultimately agrees screw it let's go back to the since 1996 he hadn't been there since 1996 so it'd been 26 years at the time

45:37.820 --> 45:44.820
wow you know and I was like man if this guy's lying we don't need any more Brad Pitts or Leonardo DiCaprio

45:44.820 --> 45:59.820
exactly and this remarkable encounter you had at this sort of food stand afterwards with this guy who's wearing a suit two guys wearing a suits and an unmarked car

45:59.820 --> 46:24.820
he walks out he walks out a lot of people in the US like to talk about this men in black phenomenon which are you could say they're the first responders when it comes to sort of alien experiences did they seem like they were human and they were coming from intelligence agencies or army affiliated or did they almost seem paranormal or alien themselves

46:24.820 --> 46:46.820
uh to me they looked normal I mean the only thing that caught my attention because I'm a short guy I'm not tall you know not big or muscular was that they were very tall okay they were about the height of someone like James or other tall strong people very military looking you know big muscular ripped

46:46.820 --> 47:01.820
I'd look up at them and like huh okay yes sir they were strong okay but if someone says oh they had weird eyes or something that's a lie a lie they were normal people okay normal human beings just strong and very well dressed

47:01.820 --> 47:16.960
only one of them spoke the other stood next to him just watching wearing sunglasses silent he didn't say a word he finished speaking they turned around and left got into the car and drove away that was when I went to look at the license plate and there wasn't one that's when all of this happened

47:16.960 --> 47:27.880
what's so remarkable to me is that they know all these personal details about you your family your address hours after you see this event and we're talking about 1996

47:27.880 --> 47:42.220
so this is really before the internet before large databases in the US let alone a small town in Brazil so have you speculated about that and thought about how did he get that information

47:42.220 --> 47:48.600
let's correct this story it wasn't hours later it was minutes later

47:48.600 --> 47:54.140
it was minutes 10-15 minutes 10-15 20 minutes at most

47:54.140 --> 47:56.500
so how does he know who you are

47:56.500 --> 48:01.460
this question you're asking me is the same question I've been asking myself for 30 years

48:01.460 --> 48:05.220
that same question I've asked myself for 30 years

48:05.220 --> 48:05.940
how

48:05.940 --> 48:09.060
because that was one of the things that terrified me the most

48:09.060 --> 48:13.040
so much so that when I went back to São Paulo and gave this interview

48:13.040 --> 48:13.700
to

48:13.700 --> 48:16.200
this ufologist

48:16.200 --> 48:17.160
nine months later

48:17.160 --> 48:18.980
I deeply regretted it

48:18.980 --> 48:21.000
because my life turned into hell

48:21.000 --> 48:24.360
at the time in Brazil

48:24.360 --> 48:26.240
all phones were landlines

48:26.240 --> 48:28.720
cell phones didn't really exist

48:28.720 --> 48:30.780
they looked like war radios you know

48:30.780 --> 48:32.920
can you read me over that kind of thing

48:32.920 --> 48:35.980
the technology was very basic just starting out

48:35.980 --> 48:39.920
so 99.99% of the population had landline phones

48:39.920 --> 48:44.880
they had the rotary dials for you to dial the numbers to make a call

48:44.880 --> 48:49.680
and I started to notice that every time I picked up the phone to talk

48:49.680 --> 48:51.660
there was someone on the other end listening

48:51.660 --> 48:57.640
because when what Claudia released aired on Globo when it leaked

48:57.640 --> 49:00.080
you could tell

49:00.080 --> 49:03.380
I even changed phone numbers and it didn't make a difference

49:03.380 --> 49:05.300
that really started to irritate me

49:05.300 --> 49:06.200
and my company

49:06.200 --> 49:07.960
inspections started showing up

49:07.960 --> 49:09.040
audits

49:09.040 --> 49:10.120
tax checks

49:10.120 --> 49:11.700
things like that

49:11.700 --> 49:15.140
you know when it feels like someone is looking for something wrong

49:15.140 --> 49:16.700
where there isn't anything

49:16.700 --> 49:19.020
in other words

49:19.020 --> 49:21.740
looking for the smallest excuse to shut you down

49:21.740 --> 49:23.440
but those inspections lasted days

49:23.440 --> 49:24.740
normally they'd last hours

49:24.740 --> 49:26.200
but these went on for days

49:26.200 --> 49:27.980
and in front of my company

49:27.980 --> 49:29.480
unmarked cars would show up

49:29.480 --> 49:30.820
cars without identification

49:30.820 --> 49:31.820
fake plates

49:31.820 --> 49:33.820
or no plates at all

49:33.820 --> 49:35.980
they'd just sit there watching, watching

49:35.980 --> 49:37.060
when you walk toward them

49:37.060 --> 49:38.240
they'd start the car and leave

49:38.240 --> 49:39.300
they never said anything

49:39.300 --> 49:41.980
and no, I was never threatened with death later

49:41.980 --> 49:42.600
that's a lie

49:42.600 --> 49:44.660
nobody ever threatened me with death

49:44.660 --> 49:46.960
but you could feel the pressure

49:46.960 --> 49:49.280
like they were saying

49:49.280 --> 49:50.320
if you keep talking

49:50.320 --> 49:51.660
things are going to get ugly

49:51.660 --> 49:55.160
something serious is going to happen to you

49:55.160 --> 49:57.700
so you were kind of harassed and intimidated

49:57.700 --> 49:59.840
do you think about

49:59.840 --> 50:02.240
these men in black characters

50:02.240 --> 50:04.520
10 to 15 minutes after

50:04.520 --> 50:05.900
is so remarkable to me

50:05.900 --> 50:07.700
I take back what I said

50:07.700 --> 50:09.440
it's not only unlikely

50:09.440 --> 50:10.900
it's impossible

50:10.900 --> 50:13.040
that they can know that information

50:13.040 --> 50:14.320
in that amount of time

50:14.320 --> 50:15.720
do you ever think

50:15.720 --> 50:16.920
that maybe they were

50:16.920 --> 50:19.180
not human themselves

50:19.180 --> 50:20.220
or they were somehow

50:20.220 --> 50:22.700
protecting or in coordination

50:22.700 --> 50:24.020
with the beings

50:24.020 --> 50:24.920
that came down

50:24.920 --> 50:26.360
in the ship and crashed?

50:26.840 --> 50:28.200
I believe I know just as much

50:28.200 --> 50:29.000
as you do, okay?

50:29.240 --> 50:30.880
It was just as surprising to me

50:30.880 --> 50:31.640
as it is to you

50:31.640 --> 50:34.680
and as I've already said before

50:34.680 --> 50:36.260
I asked myself this question

50:36.260 --> 50:37.920
thousands of times

50:37.920 --> 50:38.960
how did they get that information

50:38.960 --> 50:39.560
so quickly?

50:40.560 --> 50:42.100
I came up with a hypothesis

50:42.100 --> 50:43.520
that it might have been

50:43.520 --> 50:44.800
through my car's license plate

50:44.800 --> 50:45.600
at the time

50:45.600 --> 50:46.940
radios were very common, right?

50:47.440 --> 50:48.700
and through radio communication

50:48.700 --> 50:49.780
they may have gathered

50:49.780 --> 50:50.520
some information

50:50.520 --> 50:51.780
and started passing it along

50:51.780 --> 50:52.460
to those people

50:52.460 --> 50:54.600
that could be it

50:54.600 --> 50:55.040
now listen

50:55.040 --> 50:55.940
I'm not saying

50:55.940 --> 50:56.840
that's what happened

50:56.840 --> 50:58.600
I'm just raising a hypothesis

50:58.600 --> 51:00.640
because that was also

51:00.640 --> 51:01.280
one of the things

51:01.280 --> 51:02.700
that scared me the most

51:02.700 --> 51:03.500
at the time

51:03.500 --> 51:06.600
because the crash itself

51:06.600 --> 51:07.700
to me

51:07.700 --> 51:08.920
had been just a normal crash

51:08.920 --> 51:09.440
of an object

51:09.440 --> 51:10.900
I saw something that

51:10.900 --> 51:11.620
at that moment

51:11.620 --> 51:13.180
I thought was a government experiment

51:13.180 --> 51:15.640
something I wasn't supposed to see

51:15.640 --> 51:17.120
but when they arrived

51:17.120 --> 51:17.960
so quickly

51:17.960 --> 51:18.980
that's when I thought

51:18.980 --> 51:21.100
my God

51:21.100 --> 51:22.640
what is this?

51:23.640 --> 51:25.240
that was truly frightening

51:25.240 --> 51:27.920
and the most interesting part

51:27.920 --> 51:29.420
is that

51:29.420 --> 51:31.300
after all that process

51:31.300 --> 51:32.460
with Globo and everything

51:32.460 --> 51:33.680
being threatened and all that

51:33.680 --> 51:34.760
my wife turned to me

51:34.760 --> 51:35.060
and said

51:35.060 --> 51:36.080
look, shut up

51:36.080 --> 51:37.360
don't talk about this anymore

51:37.360 --> 51:37.880
disappear

51:37.880 --> 51:39.300
so I disappeared

51:39.300 --> 51:40.860
I changed my phone number

51:40.860 --> 51:41.620
moved houses

51:41.620 --> 51:42.740
later I returned

51:42.740 --> 51:43.460
to the same place

51:43.460 --> 51:44.340
where I live today

51:44.340 --> 51:45.960
but at the time

51:45.960 --> 51:47.400
I moved into my father's house

51:47.400 --> 51:48.800
my father

51:48.800 --> 51:50.100
who has since passed away

51:50.100 --> 51:51.300
had moved to the beach

51:51.300 --> 51:53.480
I moved into his house

51:53.480 --> 51:55.820
you see

51:55.820 --> 51:58.320
and basically erased my trail

51:58.320 --> 51:59.940
and what's interesting

51:59.940 --> 52:02.140
is that the current researcher

52:02.140 --> 52:03.040
Max Liao

52:03.040 --> 52:05.860
one day I'm at home

52:05.860 --> 52:07.020
calm and relaxed

52:07.020 --> 52:09.060
when my phone rings

52:09.060 --> 52:11.120
excuse me

52:11.120 --> 52:12.140
is this Mr. Carlos?

52:13.360 --> 52:14.160
and I thought

52:14.160 --> 52:15.140
who wants to talk to him?

52:16.140 --> 52:17.000
burned once

52:17.000 --> 52:18.240
afraid of cold water

52:18.240 --> 52:21.740
who wants to talk to him?

52:21.840 --> 52:23.340
no, please don't hang up

52:23.340 --> 52:24.640
my name is Max Liao

52:24.640 --> 52:25.840
I'm a ufologist

52:25.840 --> 52:27.020
and I'd like to talk to you

52:27.020 --> 52:28.120
about the Varginha case

52:28.120 --> 52:30.320
the reason I accepted

52:30.320 --> 52:33.660
after 26 years

52:33.660 --> 52:36.080
actually 25 years

52:36.080 --> 52:37.380
this first contact

52:37.380 --> 52:38.800
happened about a year or two earlier

52:38.800 --> 52:42.300
was because a week earlier

52:42.300 --> 52:44.760
I'd gone to a birthday party

52:44.760 --> 52:45.960
for one of my wife's cousins

52:45.960 --> 52:47.580
and I don't know where

52:47.580 --> 52:48.400
they got it from

52:48.400 --> 52:51.580
but they brought this story back up

52:51.580 --> 52:54.080
and started making fun of me

52:54.080 --> 52:55.640
some of them had been drinking

52:55.640 --> 52:56.460
a bit too much

52:56.460 --> 52:57.320
and you know

52:57.320 --> 52:58.680
drunk people have no filter

52:58.680 --> 53:02.220
they started crossing the line

53:02.220 --> 53:05.420
that made me really angry

53:05.420 --> 53:08.640
I told him

53:08.640 --> 53:09.020
I said

53:09.020 --> 53:10.320
I'll prove it to you

53:10.320 --> 53:12.440
I even cursed at him at the time

53:12.440 --> 53:13.580
used a swear word

53:13.580 --> 53:16.020
I said

53:16.020 --> 53:16.900
I'll prove to you

53:16.900 --> 53:17.900
that I'm not a liar

53:17.900 --> 53:19.040
I never lied

53:19.040 --> 53:21.200
I never gained anything from this

53:21.200 --> 53:22.320
and I won't lie now

53:22.320 --> 53:23.940
one day I'll prove it to you

53:23.940 --> 53:24.900
I'll have the proof

53:24.900 --> 53:25.900
and then sure enough

53:25.900 --> 53:27.360
Marcus called me the following week

53:27.360 --> 53:31.060
so I killed two birds with one stone

53:31.060 --> 53:31.580
I thought

53:31.580 --> 53:31.960
okay

53:31.960 --> 53:33.540
this is the moment to speak up

53:33.540 --> 53:35.020
do you know James?

53:35.180 --> 53:36.760
I didn't even know James existed

53:36.760 --> 53:38.520
I had no idea who James was

53:38.520 --> 53:38.980
nothing

53:38.980 --> 53:40.980
to be very honest

53:40.980 --> 53:43.060
my life was fine

53:43.060 --> 53:44.040
just the way it was

53:44.040 --> 53:45.820
so

53:45.820 --> 53:47.840
so I

53:47.840 --> 53:49.640
went to the house

53:49.640 --> 53:50.600
of a friend of Marcos

53:50.600 --> 53:52.180
in a neighborhood called Morumbi

53:52.180 --> 53:53.280
in São Paulo

53:53.280 --> 53:55.400
inside a very small apartment

53:55.400 --> 53:56.780
we recorded the interview

53:56.780 --> 53:57.760
I told my story

53:57.760 --> 53:58.340
he said

53:58.340 --> 53:59.640
look let's verify this

53:59.640 --> 54:00.080
I said

54:00.080 --> 54:00.760
yeah that's fine

54:00.760 --> 54:02.240
then he said

54:02.240 --> 54:02.940
wow

54:02.940 --> 54:04.620
your account is exactly the same

54:04.620 --> 54:06.500
as the one you gave 25 years ago

54:06.500 --> 54:07.420
identical

54:07.420 --> 54:09.100
not a single detail has changed

54:09.100 --> 54:09.600
I said

54:09.600 --> 54:10.040
guys

54:10.040 --> 54:11.320
I'm just telling you what I saw

54:11.320 --> 54:12.460
I don't need to lie

54:12.460 --> 54:13.920
all right

54:13.920 --> 54:14.740
okay thank you

54:14.740 --> 54:15.980
when we finished recording

54:15.980 --> 54:17.180
he tried to

54:17.180 --> 54:18.100
give me some money

54:18.100 --> 54:19.740
I told him

54:19.740 --> 54:20.360
no thank you

54:20.360 --> 54:21.180
I don't want it

54:21.180 --> 54:23.360
no I really don't want it

54:23.360 --> 54:24.480
I'm not here for money

54:24.480 --> 54:26.360
I don't need it

54:26.360 --> 54:28.100
seriously

54:28.100 --> 54:28.960
I don't need it

54:28.960 --> 54:30.480
I said

54:30.480 --> 54:31.460
do me a favor

54:31.460 --> 54:33.460
just one thing

54:33.460 --> 54:34.640
take that money

54:34.640 --> 54:35.600
and donate it

54:35.600 --> 54:36.220
to a charity

54:36.220 --> 54:37.400
that needs it

54:37.400 --> 54:39.160
because I don't need

54:39.160 --> 54:39.980
to live off this

54:39.980 --> 54:41.440
you have my word

54:41.440 --> 54:44.340
so I told him

54:44.340 --> 54:46.440
go donate it

54:46.440 --> 54:47.460
he said

54:47.460 --> 54:47.820
but

54:47.820 --> 54:48.560
I said

54:48.560 --> 54:49.500
donate it

54:49.500 --> 54:49.880
he said

54:49.880 --> 54:50.240
all right

54:50.240 --> 54:53.140
so after that

54:53.140 --> 54:54.180
I turned my back

54:54.180 --> 54:57.120
about a year later

54:57.120 --> 54:58.320
he told me

54:58.320 --> 54:59.400
that there was a filmmaker

54:59.400 --> 55:01.020
a well-known

55:01.020 --> 55:02.520
American documentary filmmaker

55:02.520 --> 55:03.940
who was coming to Brazil

55:03.940 --> 55:05.260
and wanted to meet me

55:05.260 --> 55:06.280
he said his name

55:06.280 --> 55:07.120
was James Fox

55:07.120 --> 55:08.280
I asked

55:08.280 --> 55:09.480
who is James Fox

55:09.480 --> 55:10.900
he said

55:10.900 --> 55:11.860
in the United States

55:11.860 --> 55:13.040
he's very well known

55:13.040 --> 55:13.780
you don't know him

55:13.780 --> 55:14.640
I said

55:14.640 --> 55:15.560
sorry man

55:15.560 --> 55:16.220
but I honestly

55:16.220 --> 55:17.200
have no idea

55:17.200 --> 55:19.720
then he

55:19.720 --> 55:21.660
asked me

55:21.660 --> 55:22.640
if I would agree

55:22.640 --> 55:24.040
to tell my story

55:24.040 --> 55:26.300
in the documentary

55:26.300 --> 55:27.200
I said

55:27.200 --> 55:27.560
all right

55:27.560 --> 55:29.260
and then

55:29.260 --> 55:30.440
but I made it clear

55:30.440 --> 55:32.140
I don't want to earn anything

55:32.140 --> 55:34.260
I never wanted to make money

55:34.260 --> 55:34.960
from this story

55:34.960 --> 55:36.160
I never made a single cent

55:36.160 --> 55:36.460
from it

55:36.460 --> 55:36.940
nothing

55:36.940 --> 55:38.940
because I believe

55:38.940 --> 55:39.900
the truth

55:39.900 --> 55:41.760
has to be told

55:41.760 --> 55:43.420
spoken

55:43.420 --> 55:44.900
as truth

55:44.900 --> 55:46.540
you shouldn't take advantage

55:46.540 --> 55:47.060
of others

55:47.060 --> 55:49.220
it's absurd

55:49.220 --> 55:50.040
when people

55:50.040 --> 55:51.440
have a story

55:51.440 --> 55:52.620
and exploit it

55:52.620 --> 55:54.560
charging appearance fees

55:54.560 --> 55:55.820
and things like that

55:55.820 --> 55:57.140
I mean

55:57.140 --> 55:59.100
sorry for the word

55:59.100 --> 56:02.000
but that's bad character

56:02.000 --> 56:03.260
people

56:03.260 --> 56:04.800
who take advantage

56:04.800 --> 56:05.540
of others

56:05.540 --> 56:07.920
in any situation

56:07.920 --> 56:08.640
you have to be

56:08.640 --> 56:09.360
an honest

56:09.360 --> 56:10.560
upright person

56:10.560 --> 56:11.320
with integrity

56:11.320 --> 56:12.100
one of the things

56:12.100 --> 56:12.920
I admire most

56:12.920 --> 56:13.900
about James today

56:13.900 --> 56:15.300
after getting to know him

56:15.300 --> 56:15.980
and I even say

56:15.980 --> 56:16.940
he's like a brother to me

56:16.940 --> 56:18.140
I have a special affection

56:18.140 --> 56:18.920
for him

56:18.920 --> 56:20.020
is

56:20.020 --> 56:21.560
his posture

56:21.560 --> 56:22.840
the kind of human being

56:22.840 --> 56:23.300
he is

56:23.300 --> 56:24.920
he's an upright person

56:24.920 --> 56:26.340
someone I truly

56:26.340 --> 56:28.140
admire as a human being

56:28.140 --> 56:29.920
because he's honest

56:29.920 --> 56:30.940
in what he says

56:30.940 --> 56:32.680
he only seeks

56:32.680 --> 56:33.460
the truth

56:33.460 --> 56:35.120
I've never seen him

56:35.120 --> 56:36.280
hide a lie

56:36.280 --> 56:37.780
he's the kind of guy

