it would look at us as if it were saying

01:57:21.700 --> 01:57:23.980
there's nothing but this moment anything

01:57:23.980 --> 01:57:28.260
else is another reality and it's really

01:57:28.260 --> 01:57:31.300
cool to see since you're asking me and

